{
  "stem": "210.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And it took about a week till we came, till we were sitting not in the trains, but between, you know, when the trains have like things in between.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "That's where we were sitting with three girls.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And we went back to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And it took about a week until we got back to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "But what we suffered on the way from the-- from the Russian-- you know, from the Russian soldiers-- they were constantly after us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "They were constantly wanting to-- it was just-- if we got out not raped, it was just a miracle.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And the week that we were there, there were older women.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They were sisters, two sisters, and one-- and a mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Let's say they told that they want-- the Russians, they want 10 girls for the night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And they came, and they just took 10 girls.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "If you were-- we were hiding in closets and whatever we could to avoid them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "It was the most horrible thing to go through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And there were mothers that went in order for their-- to spare their daughters or sisters.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Because one was with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "She said, I was married anyway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "If my husband survived, he wouldn't know difference if I'm a-- if I was raped or not in order to save us-- her sister, and me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And then on the train, it was constant, you know, running and fighting.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "You know, when this train stopped for a minute, you had to run.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "You have to-- not to stand in one place because you were scared.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "All you heard is Russian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And I really don't know how we made it there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And we got into Lodz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "It was the last day of Passover.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
